name: Synpunkter Allman Form Should Be Visible and Have HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
fullName: Test Cases.External Dependencies.Synpunkter Allman Form Should Be Visible and Have HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
description:
This test verifies that the feedback and complaints form is accessible from the start page,
that the form iframe is visible, and that the form responds with HTTP status 200.
Steps:
1. Navigate to Synpunkter Allmän form and check iframe is visible
2. Send a GET request to the iframe src
3. Verify that the received HTTP status code is 200.
